This Python programs calculates actual position of the choosen 
satellite from TLE elemnts in to the Azimuth-Elevation-Radius 
(AER) coordinate system.

System variables, like reveiver's position in (lat, lon, alt), usage of the 
transformation CS, WSG84 and the name of a satellite, have to the set in 
inputs.yaml configuration file.

Required libs:
- math
- yaml
- ephem
- urllib
- linecache
- numpy
- pytz
- datetime
- sgp4        https://pypi.python.org/pypi/sgp4/
